msgstr "[[s-linstor-logging]]"

#. type: Title ===
#, no-wrap
msgid "Logging"
msgstr "ロギング"

#. type: delimited block -
msgid ""
"LINSTOR uses https://www.slf4j.org/[SLF4J] with https://logback.qos.ch/"
"[logback] as binding.  This gives LINSTOR the possibility to distinguish "
"between the log levels `ERROR`, `WARN`, `INFO`, `DEBUG` and `TRACE` (in "
"order of increasing verbosity). The following are the different ways that "
"you can set the logging level, ordered by priority (first has highest "
"priority):"
msgstr ""
"LINSTORは、バインディングとして https://logback.qos.ch/[logback] を使用して"
"https://www.slf4j.org/[SLF4J]を利用しています。 これにより、LINSTORはログレベ"
"ル `ERROR`, `WARN`, `INFO`, `DEBUG`, `TRACE`（詳細度の増加順）を区別すること"
"が可能となります。ログレベルを設定するさまざまな方法は、優先順に並べると以下"
"の通りです（最初のものが最も優先度が高いです）:"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
". Since LINSTOR *client* version 1.20.1, you can use the command `controller set-log-level` to\n"
"  change the log level used by LINSTOR's running configuration. Various arguments can be used\n"
"  with this command. Refer to the command's `--help` text for details. For example, to set the\n"
"  log level to `TRACE` on the LINSTOR controller and all satellites, enter the following\n"
"  command:\n"
"+\n"
msgstr ""
".  LINSTOR *client* バージョン1.20.1以降、`controller set-log-level` コマンドを使用して、\n"
"  LINSTORの実行設定で使用されるログレベルを変更できます。このコマンドにはさまざまな引数を\n"
"  使用できます。詳細については、コマンドの `--help` テキストを参照してください。例えば、\n"
"  LINSTORコントローラーとすべてのサテライトでログレベルを `TRACE` に設定するには、\n"
"  次のコマンドを入力してください:\n"
"+\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "$ linstor controller set-log-level --global TRACE"
msgstr "$ linstor controller set-log-level --global TRACE"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"+\n"
"To change the LINSTOR log level on a particular node, you can use the LINSTOR client (since\n"
"version 1.20.1) command `node set-log-level`.\n"
"+\n"
"NOTE: Changes that you make to the log level by using the LINSTOR client will not persist\n"
"LINSTOR service restarts, for example, if a node reboots.\n"
msgstr ""
"+\n"
"特定のノードでLINSTORのログレベルを変更するには、LINSTORクライアント（バージョン1.20.1以降）の \n"
"`node set-log-level` コマンドを使用できます。\n"
"+\n"
"注意: LINSTORクライアントを使用してロギングレベルを変更した場合、\n"
"ノードが再起動するなどのデプロイメントで、設定は持続しません。\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
". `TRACE` mode can be `enabled` or `disabled` using the debug console:\n"
"+\n"
msgstr ""
". `TRACE` モードは、デバッグコンソールを使用して `enabled` または `disabled` にできます。\n"
"+\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Command ==> SetTrcMode MODE(enabled)  SetTrcMode Set TRACE level logging "
"mode New TRACE level logging mode: ENABLED"
msgstr ""
"Command ==> SetTrcMode MODE(enabled)  SetTrcMode Set TRACE level logging "
"mode New TRACE level logging mode: ENABLED"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
". When starting the controller or satellite a command line argument can be passed:\n"
"+\n"
msgstr ""
". コントローラまたはサテライトを起動するときに、コマンドライン引数を渡すことができます。\n"
"+\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"java ... com.linbit.linstor.core.Controller ... --log-level TRACE java ... "
"com.linbit.linstor.core.Satellite ... --log-level TRACE"
msgstr ""
"java ... com.linbit.linstor.core.Controller ... --log-level TRACE java ... "
"com.linbit.linstor.core.Satellite ... --log-level TRACE"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
". The recommended place is the `logging` section in the configuration file.  The default\n"
"  configuration file location is `/etc/linstor/linstor.toml` for the controller and\n"
"  `/etc/linstor/linstor_satellite.toml` for the satellite.  Configure the logging level as\n"
"  follows:\n"
"+\n"
msgstr ""
". 推奨される場所は、設定ファイル内の `logging` セクションです。コントローラのデフォルトの\n"
"設定ファイルの場所は `/etc/linstor/linstor.toml` であり、\n"
"サテライトの場合は `/etc/linstor/linstor_satellite.toml` です。\n"
"ログレベルを以下のように設定してください。\n"
"+\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   level=\"TRACE\"\n"
msgstr "   level=\"TRACE\"\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
". As LINSTOR is using logback as an implementation, `/usr/share/linstor-server/lib/logback.xml`\n"
"  can also be used. Currently only this approach supports different log levels for different\n"
"  components, like shown in the example below:\n"
"+\n"
msgstr ""
". LINSTORは実装としてlogbackを使用しているため、`/usr/share/linstor-server/lib/logback.xml` も\n"
"  使用することができます。現在、このアプローチのみが異なるコンポーネント用の異なるログレベルを\n"
"  サポートしています。その例で以下に示します。\n"
"+\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
"<configuration scan=\"false\" scanPeriod=\"60 seconds\">\n"
"<!--\n"
" Values for scanPeriod can be specified in units of milliseconds, seconds, minutes or hours\n"
" https://logback.qos.ch/manual/configuration.html\n"
"-->\n"
" <appender name=\"STDOUT\" class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.ConsoleAppender\">\n"
"   <!-- encoders are assigned the type\n"
"        ch.qos.logback.classic.encoder.PatternLayoutEncoder by default -->\n"
"   <encoder>\n"
"     <pattern>%d{HH:mm:ss.SSS} [%thread] %-5level %logger - %msg%n</pattern>\n"
"   </encoder>\n"
" </appender>\n"
" <appender name=\"FILE\" class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.RollingFileAppender\">\n"
"   <file>${log.directory}/linstor-${log.module}.log</file>\n"
"   <append>true</append>\n"
"   <encoder class=\"ch.qos.logback.classic.encoder.PatternLayoutEncoder\">\n"
"     <Pattern>%d{yyyy_MM_dd HH:mm:ss.SSS} [%thread] %-5level %logger - %msg%n</Pattern>\n"
"   </encoder>\n"
"   <rollingPolicy class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.FixedWindowRollingPolicy\">\n"
"     <FileNamePattern>logs/linstor-${log.module}.%i.log.zip</FileNamePattern>\n"
"     <MinIndex>1</MinIndex>\n"
"     <MaxIndex>10</MaxIndex>\n"
"   </rollingPolicy>\n"
"   <triggeringPolicy class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.SizeBasedTriggeringPolicy\">\n"
"     <MaxFileSize>2MB</MaxFileSize>\n"
"   </triggeringPolicy>\n"
" </appender>\n"
" <logger name=\"LINSTOR/Controller\" level=\"TRACE\" additivity=\"false\">\n"
"   <appender-ref ref=\"STDOUT\" />\n"
"   <!-- <appender-ref ref=\"FILE\" /> -->\n"
" </logger>\n"
" <logger name=\"LINSTOR/Satellite\" level=\"TRACE\" additivity=\"false\">\n"
"   <appender-ref ref=\"STDOUT\" />\n"
"   <!-- <appender-ref ref=\"FILE\" /> -->\n"
" </logger>\n"
" <root level=\"WARN\">\n"
"   <appender-ref ref=\"STDOUT\" />\n"
"   <!-- <appender-ref ref=\"FILE\" /> -->\n"
" </root>\n"
"</configuration>\n"
msgstr ""
"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n"
"<configuration scan=\"false\" scanPeriod=\"60 seconds\">\n"
"<!--\n"
" Values for scanPeriod can be specified in units of milliseconds, seconds, minutes or hours\n"
" https://logback.qos.ch/manual/configuration.html\n"
"-->\n"
" <appender name=\"STDOUT\" class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.ConsoleAppender\">\n"
"   <!-- encoders are assigned the type\n"
"        ch.qos.logback.classic.encoder.PatternLayoutEncoder by default -->\n"
"   <encoder>\n"
"     <pattern>%d{HH:mm:ss.SSS} [%thread] %-5level %logger - %msg%n</pattern>\n"
"   </encoder>\n"
" </appender>\n"
" <appender name=\"FILE\" class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.RollingFileAppender\">\n"
"   <file>${log.directory}/linstor-${log.module}.log</file>\n"
"   <append>true</append>\n"
"   <encoder class=\"ch.qos.logback.classic.encoder.PatternLayoutEncoder\">\n"
"     <Pattern>%d{yyyy_MM_dd HH:mm:ss.SSS} [%thread] %-5level %logger - %msg%n</Pattern>\n"
"   </encoder>\n"
"   <rollingPolicy class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.FixedWindowRollingPolicy\">\n"
"     <FileNamePattern>logs/linstor-${log.module}.%i.log.zip</FileNamePattern>\n"
"     <MinIndex>1</MinIndex>\n"
"     <MaxIndex>10</MaxIndex>\n"
"   </rollingPolicy>\n"
"   <triggeringPolicy class=\"ch.qos.logback.core.rolling.SizeBasedTriggeringPolicy\">\n"
"     <MaxFileSize>2MB</MaxFileSize>\n"
"   </triggeringPolicy>\n"
" </appender>\n"
" <logger name=\"LINSTOR/Controller\" level=\"TRACE\" additivity=\"false\">\n"
"   <appender-ref ref=\"STDOUT\" />\n"
"   <!-- <appender-ref ref=\"FILE\" /> -->\n"
" </logger>\n"
" <logger name=\"LINSTOR/Satellite\" level=\"TRACE\" additivity=\"false\">\n"
"   <appender-ref ref=\"STDOUT\" />\n"
"   <!-- <appender-ref ref=\"FILE\" /> -->\n"
" </logger>\n"
" <root level=\"WARN\">\n"
"   <appender-ref ref=\"STDOUT\" />\n"
"   <!-- <appender-ref ref=\"FILE\" /> -->\n"
" </root>\n"
"</configuration>\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"See the https://logback.qos.ch/manual/index.html[logback manual] to find more details about\n"
"`logback.xml`.\n"
msgstr ""
"See the https://logback.qos.ch/manual/index.html[logback manual] to find more details about\n"
"`logback.xml`.\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid "When none of the configuration methods above is used LINSTOR will default to `INFO` log level.\n"
msgstr "上記の設定方法のいずれも使用されない場合、LINSTOR はデフォルトで `INFO` ログレベルになります。\n"

