" * `resource`\n"
" * `storage_pools`\n"
" * `error_reports`\n"

#. type: delimited block -
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"These all default to `true`. To disable, for example, error report data use:\n"
"`http://localhost:3370/metrics?error_reports=false`.\n"
